    "text": "\"How do I deal with the kid who doesn't want to be there?\"\n\nThis comes up constantly.\n\nMy approach:\n\n1. Find out WHY they don't want to be there\n2. Give them a role (even a small one)\n3. Catch them doing something right\n4. Talk to them like a human\n\nMost \"problem\" kids just want to feel valued.\n\nBuild your coaching identity. Join 1,500+ coaches → link in bio"
