    "text": "No one wants to help coach.\n\nThe few who do, quit after a month.\n\nHere's what works:\n\nDon't ask for commitment. Ask for one session.\n\n\"Can you help Thursday?\" beats \"Can you be assistant coach?\"\n\nLower the barrier. Build relationships. Commitment follows."
