    "text": "The 4-3-3 formation dominates modern football.\n\nBut teaching it to youth players requires understanding: when players are ready for it, how to teach each position's role, how to adapt it for different ages, and common mistakes to avoid.\n\nThe complete 4-3-3 youth guide.\n\nRead more: 360tft.co.uk"
